{"tid":1745576,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"六四逃亡者籲啟動救援港人方案　報答89年救命之恩","createTime":"2019-11-22T09:46:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T12:07:15.000Z","uid":48093,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b1876f118537cd982b00fdbbd0fb1ec91a9de796","tid":1745576,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:46:33.000Z","msg":"「黃雀行動」及六四事件後逃亡海外人士就近日香港警方圍攻大學發表聯署聲明，表示反送中示威運動愈演愈烈，但香港政府無視民意，一意孤行，鎮壓暴力不斷升級，近日警察更圍攻中文大學及理工大學，和平校園猶如戰場。<br />\n<br />\n聲明提出4項要求及呼籲，包括要求特區政府立即停止進一步鎮壓，承認錯誤，允許獨立調查，恢復法治；其次要求盡快釋放所有被捕學生及市民，追究警方責任。<br />\n<br />\n他們呼籲香港學生不要再犧牲，留得青山，以期喚起民眾，做長期抗爭準備；亦呼籲整合資源，疏通管道，啟動救援香港人的方案，以期付諸實施，報答香港人30年前「黃雀行動」的救命之恩。<br />\n<br />\n聲明的首批簽署人包括，吾爾開希、嚴家其、高皋、封從德、蘇曉康等。"},{"pid":"db913ff7e83d72fec5976fda32c10dede36ea5c5","tid":1745576,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"103b6726b51bf7820bb0015ccb464e3f1d4b825a","tid":1745576,"uid":19151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd44c8d618fa84a2bf80f92cd6b7a25a800e3db","tid":1745576,"uid":152455,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:50:02.000Z","msg":"真中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3636569da970bdaa57852806b87b7dc9ea54ca","tid":1745576,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295bb391064699a4638e2fee9fa238434a5fec50","tid":1745576,"uid":120555,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:51:45.000Z",